the other day i typed this into my profile:

I've never realized just how hard growing up was until i realized that the people i've loved and grown up  with my entire life started to leave one by one out of this town and into their new lives. i miss you already everyone!

the sad thing is.. not everyone has left yet.. and not everyone is going to leave.. i feel like i have wasted an entire summer working and not being able to spend time with those who i have been with my entire life pretty much.. i havent seen half the people i have wanted to see and i wont get that chance until december vacation..

i know it seems really sad and all.. but yeah.. i havent started college yet so maybe ill change my mind once i go myself.. and make new friends.. but i just hate it when i look at  a friends away message that has left and it mentions something like "out making new friends".. im scared i wont make new friends when im at fitchburg.. and to tell u the truth i dont really want to.. i hate change.. and i know its goign to happen whether or not i want it to.. but yeah.. i wish i was living at college because then i'd know what everyone is talking about when i talk to them. also its kinda sad too that i miss people.. but i really miss people that i only talk to once and a while.. but yeah.. blah.. its going to be a very lonely town for the next couple months

while.. im so going to miss him!!.. zack even started to dance i was so shocked lol.. hes the greatest!!.. so yeah it was one of the most memorable nights of my life.. and although everyone thought iwas completely trashed i wasnt.. i was just having a really good time lol.. and i kept my sunglasses on because they are prescription lol ok well thats all for now.. so long.. todays practice at the park.. and then bacalariout is tonight.. then maybe off to steves im not sure yet though.. ok well  byes

So it really hasnt hit me yet that the class of 2004 is out of school.... it hasnt hit me yet that we will never be in the same school again..all together.. i still keep thinking that tuesday morning we will be back in the same classes.. and ill get to see my friends everyday. .. but we wont.. i mean yeah we will see each other again.. its not like we never will.. but it just wont ever be the same... i was talking to my old friend.. and he told me that i am in for many big changes.. and i guess i've always known that after highschools over i will be faced with changes.. but i never knew how fast high school would end.. i know everyone says "i hate highschool".. and somedays i feel that way too... but then i look back on it like i have done for the passed few days.. and i realized how much i actually loved highschool..  and its all because of the people that i went with.. i love my friends to death.. and im so going to miss not seeing them everyday in class.. .. im going to miss not having sewing w/ ashley and maya.. it was alwasy a good time.. all we ever did was laugh...  im going to miss 3rd period studies .. and even though i havent realy hung out with some of the people in the study.. we alwasy had a good time... and although we have all changed i will always remember the times we all hung out together..  6th period with katlyn i will miss.. Mrs Lents english class.. where although sometimes i wanted to shoot everyone in that class.. i've relized just how much fun that class truly was because of all the guys.. .. then yearbook.. what can i say abotu that.. me jess, maya, beth, alicia, stacy, sean, jenna.. it was an awesome time. so many funny things happening...  how im going to miss all of it.. and i know that every school year u think back on all the good times... but i can proudly say that senior year was definatly one of my best years to remember.. .. there will never be another class like the class of 2004.... nothign will ever replace it.. and although when we graduate from college we will feel just as important being the class of 2008.... it will never compare with our lil class of 120 or so kids.. who have pretty much grown up together... and have seen each other grow up into amazing adults.       i love the class of 2004.. and although we have 1 more week together.. i will miss you dearly...

Graduation: june 5th

Graduation Party: June 11th.. my house.. anyone want to come who wasnt invited just let me know.. im so up for whoever at my party... love yas

i've been thinking about it lately.. and i really really wish i could go far far away for college.. i would so give anything to move away.. not for ever.. but just a long enough time for me to meet new people.. and become friends w/ new people.. dont get me wrong.. i love my friends.. but its just different.. its like im yearning to get away from this place.. from people i've known my entire friggen life.. i love this place.. and i love the people i know but im just so sick of some of the fucking shit that goes on in this town.. im sick of everyone knowing everything that goes on.. im sick of drama.. im sick of people blowing up about nothing at all..   i think i really just need a long ass vacation.. and its not comign soon enough.. i mean i want to hang out w/ everyone this summer.. its probably our last summer that we are all friends.. or see each other.. i want to go up to the beach.. and i want to hang out.. its just hard.. i think that its kinda like what mayas lj said one time.. that shes been thinking about college and shit... and although i wish i was going far far away.. i look back at what i just wrote.. and i wish no one was leave.. i just wish some of the fucked up issues that happen during highschool that shouldnt happen wouldnt.. i wish we could all stay together for another year or so... w/ out the bullshit... and stuff.. its going to be so different and i dont think im ready for it.. i mean i know i am.. but it just kinda sucks not being able to see .. i think i wrote that i wish i was far far away just beacuse i know ill be one of the only few that are going to be left here.. i think if i was going away.. i wouldnt feel so weird because i know everyoen else is away.. but right now all i know is ill be home.. and maybe a few others will be too.. but it just wont be the same.. god growing up sucks.. lol.. anyways enough of that.. sorry had to vent.. im just so confused about people in general.. but whatever..  so anyways...
